main event: An unknown flying object was observed by at least five people at Carswell AFB, Texas on 29 July 1965 at 2030 hours CST.
interesting points: The UFO flew through the Carswell AFB Control Zone at a low altitude without position lights., The object had at least three brilliant flashing white lights and was completely silent during flight., The sighting lasted for approximately 10 to 15 minutes., The object appeared to be the size of a baseball bat when observed closely., The sighting was corroborated by three other individuals on duty.
sighted object: an unknown flying object with flashing white lights
witness description: A command pilot who is a Major in the USAFR and has a Top Secret clearance.
